description:
Bobby has the show try and identity the Top 10 richest females in country music in this week’s Bobby Feud. Bobby, Amy, Eddie and Lunchbox all have 60 seconds to share what they are currently nerding out on. Plus, Lunchbox had a dream and big revelation with his trip to California to be on big game shows.
